tton\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" aria-label=\"다음 슬라이드로 이동\" aria-disabled=\"false\">\n            <span class=\"is-blind\">다음 슬라이드로 가기</span>\n          </button>\n        <span class=\"swiper-notification\" aria-live=\"assertive\" aria-atomic=\"true\"></span></div>\n      </div>\n      <ul class=\"c-bullet-type-circle -mt-8n-2\">\n        <li class=\"refer\">주민등록번호와 외국인 등록번호는 처음 한 번만 입력하면 돼요. 앱에 저장되지 않으니 안심하세요.</li>\n      </ul>\n\n      <p class=\"h4 fw-m -mt-8n-5\">가입제한설정</p>\n      <div class=\"m-swiper swiper_swiper2-3 swiperPc-nav -mt-8n-2\">\n        <div class=\"swiper-container swiper-container-initialized swiper-container-horizontal\">\n          <div class=\"swiper-wrapper\" style=\"transition-duration: 0ms;\">\n            <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n              <ul class=\"cv-thumb-list type-step\">\n                <li>\n                  <p class=\"th-label\">1단계</p>\n                  <p class=\"th-thumb\">\n                  </p>\n                  <p class=\"th-cont\">PASS앱 [전체] → [명의도용방지] → [가입제한설정]을 누르세요.</p>\n                </li>\n                <li>\n                  <p class=\"th-label\">2단계</p>\n                  <p class=\"th-thumb\">\n                  </p>\n                  <p class=\"th-cont\">주민등록번호 또는 외국인 등록번호 뒤 6자리를<br>입력하세요.</p>\n                </li>\n                <li>\n                  <p class=\"th-label\">3단계</p>\n                  <p class=\"th-thumb\">\n                  </p>\n                  <p class=\"th-cont\">고유식별정보 처리에 동의하고 [확인]을 누르세요.</p>\n                </li>\n              </ul>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n              <ul class=\"cv-thumb-list type-step\">\n                <li>\n                  <p class=\"th-label\">4단계</p>\n                  <p class=\"th-thumb\">\n                  </p>\n                  <p class=\"th-cont\">[설정하기]를 누르세요.</p>\n                </li>\n                <li>\n                  <p class=\"th-label\">5단계</p>\n                  <p class=\"th-thumb\">\n                  </p>\n                  <p class=\"th-cont\">제한하고 싶은 통신사 옆의 스위치를 켜고<br>[완료]를 누르세요.</p>\n                </li>\n                <li>\n                  <p class=\"th-label\">6단계</p>\n                  <p class=\"th-thumb\">\n                  </p>\n                  <p class=\"th-cont\">통신사별 설정 결과를 확인할 수 있어요.</p>\n                </li>\n              </ul>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <button class=\"swiper-button-prev\" type=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" aria-label=\"이전 슬라이드로 이동\" aria-disabled=\"false\">\n            <span class=\"is-blind\">이전 슬라이드로 가기</span>\n          </button>\n          <button class=\"swiper-button-next\" type=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" aria-label=\"다음 슬라이드로 이동\" aria-disabled=\"false\">\n            <span class=\"is-blind\">다음 슬라이드로 가기</span>\n          </button>\n        <span class=\"swiper-notification\" aria-live=\"assertive\" aria-atomic=\"true\"></span></div>\n      </div>\n      <ul class=\"c-bullet-type-circle -mt-8n-2\">\n        <li class=\"refer\">주민등록번호와 외국인 등록번호는 처음 한 번만 입력하면 돼요. 앱에 저장되지 않으니 안심하세요.</li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  \n  <!-- //CVHTML : 이용방법 -->\n</div> <!----> <!----></div><!----><!----></div></div></div>\n<hr class=\"section-divider\">\n<div class=\"c-accordion-group\"><div variant=\"primary\" class=\"c-accordion-header collapsed\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"_uid_421_1\" style=\"overflow-anchor: none;\"><div class=\"row\" style=\"width: 100%;\"><div class=\"col\"><strong>가입 및 해지</strong></div> <!----></div> <div class=\"acc-toggle\"><i class=\"when-open\"></i> <i class=\"when-closed\"></i></div></div> <div id=\"_uid_421_1\" class=\"collapse\" style=\"display: none;\"><div class=\"card\"><!----><!----><div class=\"card-body\"><!----><!---->\n\n<div class=\"cv-html-wrap\">\n  <!-- CVHTML : 가입 및 해지 -->\n  <div class=\"pc-cv-box\">\n\n    <div class=\"cv-use-wrap\">\n      <p cl